{"tid":769072,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼聯新10號誕生！接班碧咸伊巴謙莫域 摩帥真能靠他？","createTime":"2018-08-06T02:05:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T04:08:23.000Z","uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"7c84bb99f654a416ee4031da9a485c18ae56f04d","tid":769072,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T02:05:18.000Z","msg":"　　曼聯在與拜仁的熱身賽比賽中，小將拉舒福特身披10號球衣亮相。在賽後，曼聯正式宣佈新賽季拉舒福特的波衫號碼為10號。<br />\n<br />\n　　上季回歸曼聯的伊巴謙莫域身著10號波衫，伊巴謙莫域離隊後曼聯的10號波衫空缺。新賽季開始，球隊的英格蘭本土新星拉舒福特將會身穿10號波衫，這也意味著他將身擔球隊的重任。<br />\n<br />\n　　此前10號波衫的主人包括威爾斯傳奇前鋒馬克-修斯，荷蘭神鋒雲尼斯達萊，朗尼以及舒寧咸等球員。碧咸在穿上7號波衫之前，也是身著10號。<br />\n<br />\n  新賽季身披球隊如此具有重量級的號碼，不知拉舒福特能否抗住這個重任。"},{"pid":"eccfe022e1ad660b4f9fc17ca1a748b667ef31c8","tid":769072,"uid":34525,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T02:22:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"237d1ed67ae429168297c14999ebec33b03ce012","tid":769072,"uid":2033,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T02:42:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6b29ac71dc1424e892f2e863d4681b3bf202c54","tid":769072,"uid":886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"237d1ed67ae429168297c14999ebec33b03ce012","tid":769072,"uid":2033,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T02:42:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T02:42:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bb2c187d5e65563a95e121d493826ae85f853a4","tid":769072,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018